Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:11.12,ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H008080ff}{\frz-90}通向月亮的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:17.86,ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ffff}君は眠り　夢を解く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:17.86,ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ffff}{\frz-90}你恬然沉睡 梦境已被解开
