Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.98,0:21:45.96,ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ffff}気づいて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.98,0:21:45.96,ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ffff}{\frz-90}你要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:48.83,ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ff80}I'm here waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:48.83,ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ff80}{\frz-90}我在这里等待着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:51.95,ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H00ffff80}今とは違う未来があっても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:51.95,ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H00ffff80}{\frz-90}即使身处不同的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:54.55,ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0088aeff}I'm here waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:54.55,ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0088aeff}{\frz-90}我在这里等待着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:57.61,ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H008080ff}叫び続けて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:57.61,ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H008080ff}{\frz-90}不停的呼喊着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.14,0:22:03.87,ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ffff}きっと心は繋ぐ糸を手繰ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.14,0:22:03.87,ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ffff}{\frz-90}一定可以追寻回维系彼此心灵的纽带
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:08.92,ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ff80}あの頃の私目を覚ますのように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:08.92,ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ff80}{\frz-90}等到那时请将我唤醒
